{"tid":2063843,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【逾百套流出】高雄職校驚見學生集體裸照 校方緊急回收畢業紀念冊","createTime":"2020-06-14T10:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T11:28:03.000Z","uid":27064,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e83dfad4cfe25422c5954ed4487d4d4cb4119148","tid":2063843,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T10:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/BGg9MHjfOi-u_4AlMh44fDRHynU=/760x544/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GUAEMGPVPNRYYHVFV2YN56V7PM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBGg9MHjfOi-u_4AlMh44fDRHynU%3D%2F760x544%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGUAEMGPVPNRYYHVFV2YN56V7PM.jpg&h=7bc5f5f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/2g-EaoXUsphcZ3F8JaZbH2b4-mc=/760x509/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LUKFEQFMAJ47PQRWNM7XVXSDZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2g-EaoXUsphcZ3F8JaZbH2b4-mc%3D%2F760x509%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLUKFEQFMAJ47PQRWNM7XVXSDZA.jpg&h=4d86a36d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/0Aa9_jyHHiiRWWvefJXyZMhDdgM=/760x1050/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LR5TE7UGSEHSGUP6LPVORMNKOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0Aa9_jyHHiiRWWvefJXyZMhDdgM%3D%2F760x1050%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLR5TE7UGSEHSGUP6LPVORMNKOU.jpg&h=1e05b35f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n驪歌響起進入畢業季，不過台灣高雄一所高職畢業紀念冊竟出現5張不雅照，其中甚至出現9位男學生只遮第三點的全裸照，與有學生脫光衣物躺在浴缸裡，校方得知後緊急回收畢業紀念冊與光碟，但所發出去的909套，至今只回收786套，仍有123套流傳在外，高市教育局表示，將督促學校日後相關紀念冊或文宣，須建立檢核機制，勿再發生類似情況。<br />\n<br />\n這間公立職校，在高雄頗負盛名、歷史攸久，但有讀者爆料，今年的畢業紀念冊裡，有兩個班級張貼了不雅照片，包括有位男同學連續有兩張全裸躺在浴缸照片，第三點用手遮住，另有9位男同學在廁所裡全裸排排站，只將第三點以手或其他方式遮掩，還有男同學全裸露臀等5張照片。<br />\n<br />\n校方表示，該校是在上月17日接獲民眾反映畢業紀念冊有不雅照，隨即進行了解，並在5月22日召開性別平等教育委員會，當中學生委員代表，認為照片沒露第三點還好，不過，多數委員還是認為照片不妥，因此決議將畢業紀念冊與電子光碟全數回收，將不雅照片部分用貼紙及檔案遮罩，再發還學生。<br />\n<br />\n校方表示，學校畢業紀念冊分為共同頁及各班級的部分，共同頁由校方行政單位校對；各班級的內容則由導師和製作學生審視及校對，對出現不雅照，有詢問兩位審核的班級導師，一位認為沒有不妥，另一位則指認為不妥，但仍尊重學生創意，因此造成有兩個班級出現不妥照情況。<br />\n<br />\n高市教育局表示，校方在5月17日知道此事，隨即依據「性別平等教育法」規定在24小時內進行校安通報，並決議畢業紀念冊全數回收，將不雅照片部分用貼紙遮罩，該局也將督促學校爾後相關紀念冊或文宣等資料，須建立檢核機制，加強把關。<br />\n台灣《蘋果動新聞》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200612/7KPFOPHU2FOZXWTYDXTXTFYHBM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200612%2F7KPFOPHU2FOZXWTYDXTXTFYHBM%2F&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJtUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=75cee1c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200612%2F7KPFOPHU2FOZXWTYDXTXTFYHBM%2F&h=46ca7db2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200612/7KPFOPHU2FOZXWTYDXTXTFYHBM/</a>"},{"pid":"c1635cefbe6313c3ec8ad046336f9fc305658d00","tid":2063843,"uid":17545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e83dfad4cfe25422c5954ed4487d4d4cb4119148","tid":2063843,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T10:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/BGg9MHjfOi-u_4AlMh44fDRHynU=/760x544/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GUAEMGPVPNRYYHVFV2YN56V7PM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBGg9MHjfOi-u_4AlMh44fDRHynU%3D%2F760x544%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGUAEMGPVPNRYYHVFV2YN56V7PM.jpg&h=7bc5f5f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/2g-EaoXUsphcZ3F8JaZbH2b4-mc=/760x509/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LUKFEQFMAJ47PQRWNM7XVXSDZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2g-EaoXUsphcZ3F8JaZbH2b4